         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">22/11/87 ¶ The Acacia, which you raised from seeds near Sea-Range, ¶  dear Mr Bailey, is an  ¶ entirely new species, ¶  and particularly beautiful too! I have named it in honor of yourself. Shall I pu...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.11.22</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Bailey</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Queensland Herbarium, Brisbane.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Acacia">Acacia</name> baileyana</seg> (BRI-AQ0022725).</p>
               </note>22/11/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The <name key="Acacia">Acacia</name>, which you raised from seeds near Sea-Range,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Qld. MS note by Bailey also with specimen: 'In flower at Bowen Park Aug 1876 in some respects this species is like A. polybotrya in others it resembles A. decurrens but the pod must be [waited] for The plant was raised from seed given to me by the Postman (Walker) at Cardwell[.] FMB'. See also F. Bailey to M, 1887 (in this edition as 87-00-00d). </p>
               </note> dear Mr Bailey, is an <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">entirely new species,</hi>
               </seg> and particularly beautiful too! I have named it in honor of yourself. Shall I publish the description here or send it to <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">you</hi>
               </seg>?<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's description was published in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions</seg> of the Royal Society of Victoria (B88.07.03, p. 168).</p>
               </note> What a pity, that it cannot at once be put into the Atlas<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B87.13.04, B88.13.01.</p>
               </note> for want of fruits.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Acacia">Acacia</name>
            </p>
